pdfspine — bundled Noto symbol fonts NOTICE
===========================================

This product includes three Noto font faces, embedded into the renderer as
permissive substitute glyph outlines for the two non-embedded *pictographic*
standard-14 fonts (Symbol and ZapfDingbats):

  - Noto Sans Math      (Regular) — Symbol primary
  - Noto Sans Symbols 2 (Regular) — ZapfDingbats primary; Symbol supplement
  - Noto Sans Symbols   (Regular) — ZapfDingbats supplement

